So I managed to come up with an entirely new solution in a weekend and figured out how to use the abstract syntax tree to work through.

00:07:28.340 --> 00:07:30.740
And so I built an entirely new version of it.

00:07:30.740 --> 00:07:34.280
And that is what is currently available in NumPyDoc.

